attributes.additional_details:
Adherence to SCV2-prevention rules has been sub-optimal so far. This measure would:

1. Help to contain the spread of Sars-Cov-2;

2. Introduce a sense of urgency and inescapability from rules - which might psychologically spillover to other areas of distancing that are more difficult to enforce;

3. Foster a much needed sense of duty, fairness and community in the population;

4. Allow Britain to set an example of efficiency and pragmatism, leading the way globally, as per its best tradition.
